replies.body:
Yoona and Kokua both make excellent points, so much so that I won't bear repeating their words and stealing their thunder.

Another thing to keep in mind that I can think of is that, until just recently, Lulu was one of the most meta Support Champions during the 'Rush Ardent Support' meta. With that said a lot of players will try to use her with that in mind, and thus that means you'll have more players to compete against in order to prove your skill. I can say though from what I see your Lulu games aren't too shabby, so keep up the pressure and I'm sure you'll nab a solid S in no time!
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
